  <h2>Conclusion</h2>

  <p>Portuguese stands well-positioned for the 21st century, supported by demographic trends, economic opportunities, and cultural vitality. The language's growing digital presence, expanding business applications, and rich cultural production suggest a vibrant future.</p>

